data.description: Calling All Buyers!!! This BEAUTIFUL home nestled in a Golf Community located in Tamarac is ready for a new OWNER.  Come and enjoy this home with your family and friends.  The stunning view from your screened-in patio will be a feature you and your family will love!  This great Community & Convenient Location is close to shopping, schools & entertainment. This Home does have a new roof completed in December 2023 and Home is Equipped with Hurricane Impact Doors and Windows through the Pace Program.  Bring All Offers!!!
